response.overview: From Woodside, NY 11377 - 01.19.2019.  The Main Event – Non-Title (Johnny Gargano vs. EVOLVE Champion Austin Theory); Grudge Match (EVOLVE Tag Team Champion Montez Ford vs. Eddie Kingston); #1 Contender’s Match (AR Fox with Ayla & The Skulk vs. Anthony Henry); Hoss Fight (EVOLVE Tag Team Champion Angelo Dawkins vs. Josh Briggs); Non-Title Match (WWN Champion JD Drake vs. Joe Gacy); Four Way Freestyle (Darby Allin vs. Curt Stallion vs. Leon Ruff vs. BSHP KN); Plus more with former EVOLVE Champion Fabian Aichner, Priscilla Kelly and others!!!
